{"tid":1834048,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"6.12遭警射中右眼 女拔教師入稟控警方不合法武力","createTime":"2020-01-22T08:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T08:22:06.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f3ec49d2bd05f60d2e59fa90c16ce95cf9d35e","tid":1834048,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:22:06.000Z","msg":"去年6.12警方於金鐘以催淚彈及布袋彈等武器，驅散反送中示威者。其中拔萃女書院通識科教師楊子俊遭警方的子彈射中右眼，致其右眼僅餘2.5%視力。楊日前入稟區域法院，指控警方施加不合法武力，認為警方違反《基本法》及《警察通例》，令他人身受損害，故向警務處處長鄧炳強索償。<br />\n<br />\n原告楊子俊，被告則是由律政司代表的警務處處長。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀透露，警方去年6月12日於金鐘紅棉路與夏愨道交界對原告施加不合法武力，而該侵權及不合法行為違反《基本法》第28、39條、以及《警察通例》第29條所載關於武力及槍械使用之宣告，現就被告導致原告人身傷害等侵權行為索償。<br />\n<br />\n楊於本月3日晚上出席教協的「無懼白色恐怖，堅守教師專業」集會，當晚他已聲言會向警方提出申索，並要求警方公佈使用武力的準則。他呼籲當日在場人士提供相關相片或影片。楊於去年6月12日原本遭拘捕以暴動罪名，較早前踢保成功。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：DCPI219/19】<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/UM3hRrjLlmxZDpvyw1WDSiavGss=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/XILMD5G6BY6J4QQ75FJSHUYGWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FUM3hRrjLlmxZDpvyw1WDSiavGss%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FXILMD5G6BY6J4QQ75FJSHUYGWQ.jpg&h=543fb240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200122/PUWZKADP6FDVJB55EJC52D7VAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200122%2FPUWZKADP6FDVJB55EJC52D7VAM%2F&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzW%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=082c8800\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200122%2FPUWZKADP6FDVJB55EJC52D7VAM%2F&h=b1081fea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200122/PUWZKADP6FDVJB55EJC52D7VAM/</a>"}]}